      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a pristine BMW E46 M3, a masterclass in naturally aspirated engineering. The high-revving S54 inline-six remains the centerpiece, featuring individual throttle bodies and a precision-tuned double-VANOS system for optimal variable valve timing. This example boasts a factory-correct Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox with crisp synchro engagement and a variable M differential lock that ensures maximum lateral traction. The chassis is structurally flawless, with no fatigue at the rear subframe mounting points. Performance is bolstered by an aluminum multi-link rear suspension and MacPherson struts up front, providing telepathic feedback. Meticulously preserved, the mechanical tolerances and compression numbers are consistent with a showroom-floor specimen.",
