      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional find: a collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage, resulting in a paint finish that is deep, lustrous, and free of the common swirl marks or stone chips found on lesser examples. Inside, the cabin remains a time-capsule; the premium leather seats show zero bolster wear, and the factory-fresh scent still lingers. Every button, switch, and electronic feature functions with tactile precision. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive service history with all maintenance performed ahead of schedule by certified technicians. Under the hood, the engine bay is spotless, and the undercarriage remains pristine. This is not just a used car; it is an investment-quality piece for the discerning enthusiast who demands perfection without compromise. Includes all original keys, manuals, and a complete folder of maintenance documentation.",
